Once you've sent the funds to the above address, the SDK will monitor this address for unspent confirmed outputs and use a trustless submarine swap to receive these into your Lightning node. You can always monitor the status of the current in-progress swap using the following code: Rust let swap_info = sdk.in_progress_swap().await?; Swift let swapInfo = try? sdk.inProgressSwap() Kotlin try { val swapInfo = sdk.inProgressSwap()
